## Installation

```bash
# Clone the repo
git clone https://github.com/your-org/{{ name }}.git
cd {{ name }}

# Install dependencies
{% if package_manager == "npm" %}npm install
{% elif package_manager == "pnpm" %}pnpm install
{% elif package_manager == "yarn" %}yarn install
{% elif package_manager == "pip" %}pip install -r requirements.txt
{% elif package_manager == "go modules" %}go mod download
{% elif package_manager == "cargo" %}cargo build
{% endif %}

# Set up environment variables
cp .env.example .env
# Edit .env with your values
```

